{
  "book": "1nephi",
  "bookName": "1 Nephi",
  "chapter": 15,
  "voice": {
    "provider": "elevenlabs",
    "voice_id": "ddDFRErfhdc2asyySOG5",
    "model_id": "eleven_multilingual_v2",
    "settings": {
      "stability": 0.5,
      "similarity_boost": 0.75,
      "style": 0.35,
      "use_speaker_boost": true
    },
    "name": "Samuel"
  },
  "pauses": {
    "line_ms": 180,
    "verse_ms": 500
  },
  "duration": 525.549,
  "lines": [
    {
      "start": 0.0,
      "end": 3.808,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And then after I, Nephi, had been carried away in the Spirit,",
      "verse": "15:1",
      "lineIndex": 1
    },
    {
      "start": 3.988,
      "end": 5.799,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and seen all these things,",
      "verse": "15:1",
      "lineIndex": 2
    },
    {
      "start": 5.979,
      "end": 8.347,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "I returned to the tent of my father.",
      "verse": "15:1",
      "lineIndex": 3
    },
    {
      "start": 9.027,
      "end": 10.838,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And then I saw my brothers,",
      "verse": "15:2",
      "lineIndex": 4
    },
    {
      "start": 11.018,
      "end": 13.34,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and they were disputing one with another",
      "verse": "15:2",
      "lineIndex": 5
    },
    {
      "start": 13.52,
      "end": 16.817,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "concerning the things which my father had spoken to them.",
      "verse": "15:2",
      "lineIndex": 6
    },
    {
      "start": 17.497,
      "end": 20.423,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "For he truly spoke many great things to them,",
      "verse": "15:3",
      "lineIndex": 7
    },
    {
      "start": 20.603,
      "end": 22.739,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which were hard to be understood,",
      "verse": "15:3",
      "lineIndex": 8
    },
    {
      "start": 22.919,
      "end": 25.334,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "save a man should inquire of the Lord;",
      "verse": "15:3",
      "lineIndex": 9
    },
    {
      "start": 25.514,
      "end": 27.604,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and they being hard in their hearts,",
      "verse": "15:3",
      "lineIndex": 10
    },
    {
      "start": 27.784,
      "end": 30.71,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "therefore they did not look to the Lord as they ought.",
      "verse": "15:3",
      "lineIndex": 11
    },
    {
      "start": 31.39,
      "end": 33.898,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And now I, Nephi, was grieved",
      "verse": "15:4",
      "lineIndex": 12
    },
    {
      "start": 34.078,
      "end": 36.632,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "because of the hardness of their hearts,",
      "verse": "15:4",
      "lineIndex": 13
    },
    {
      "start": 36.812,
      "end": 39.923,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and also, because of the things which I had seen,",
      "verse": "15:4",
      "lineIndex": 14
    },
    {
      "start": 40.103,
      "end": 42.797,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and knew they must unavoidably come to pass",
      "verse": "15:4",
      "lineIndex": 15
    },
    {
      "start": 42.977,
      "end": 46.506,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "because of the great wickedness of the children of men.",
      "verse": "15:4",
      "lineIndex": 16
    },
    {
      "start": 47.186,
      "end": 50.483,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And then I was overcome because of my hardships,",
      "verse": "15:5",
      "lineIndex": 18
    },
    {
      "start": 50.663,
      "end": 54.146,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for I considered that my afflictions were great above all,",
      "verse": "15:5",
      "lineIndex": 19
    },
    {
      "start": 54.326,
      "end": 56.694,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "because of the destruction of my people,",
      "verse": "15:5",
      "lineIndex": 20
    },
    {
      "start": 56.874,
      "end": 58.685,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for I had seen their fall.",
      "verse": "15:5",
      "lineIndex": 21
    },
    {
      "start": 59.365,
      "end": 61.594,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And then after I had received strength",
      "verse": "15:6",
      "lineIndex": 22
    },
    {
      "start": 61.774,
      "end": 63.307,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "I spoke to my brothers,",
      "verse": "15:6",
      "lineIndex": 23
    },
    {
      "start": 63.487,
      "end": 66.877,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "desiring to know of them the cause of their disputations.",
      "verse": "15:6",
      "lineIndex": 24
    },
    {
      "start": 67.557,
      "end": 72.665,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And they said: Behold, we cannot understand the words which our father has spoken",
      "verse": "15:7",
      "lineIndex": 25
    },
    {
      "start": 72.845,
      "end": 76.189,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "concerning the natural branches of the olive tree,",
      "verse": "15:7",
      "lineIndex": 26
    },
    {
      "start": 76.369,
      "end": 78.737,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and also concerning the Gentiles.",
      "verse": "15:7",
      "lineIndex": 27
    },
    {
      "start": 79.417,
      "end": 80.903,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And I said to them:",
      "verse": "15:8",
      "lineIndex": 28
    },
    {
      "start": 81.083,
      "end": 82.894,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Have you inquired of the Lord?",
      "verse": "15:8",
      "lineIndex": 29
    },
    {
      "start": 83.574,
      "end": 85.06,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And they said to me:",
      "verse": "15:9",
      "lineIndex": 30
    },
    {
      "start": 85.24,
      "end": 86.726,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "We have not;",
      "verse": "15:9",
      "lineIndex": 31
    },
    {
      "start": 86.906,
      "end": 89.553,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for the Lord makes no such thing known to us.",
      "verse": "15:9",
      "lineIndex": 32
    },
    {
      "start": 90.233,
      "end": 91.858,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Behold, I said to them:",
      "verse": "15:10",
      "lineIndex": 33
    },
    {
      "start": 92.038,
      "end": 95.149,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "How is it that you do not keep the commandments of the Lord?",
      "verse": "15:10",
      "lineIndex": 34
    },
    {
      "start": 95.329,
      "end": 97.372,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "How is it that you will perish,",
      "verse": "15:10",
      "lineIndex": 35
    },
    {
      "start": 97.552,
      "end": 99.874,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "because of the hardness of your hearts?",
      "verse": "15:10",
      "lineIndex": 36
    },
    {
      "start": 100.554,
      "end": 103.433,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Do you not remember the things which the Lord has said?\u2014",
      "verse": "15:11",
      "lineIndex": 37
    },
    {
      "start": 103.613,
      "end": 106.957,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "If you will not harden your hearts, and ask me in faith,",
      "verse": "15:11",
      "lineIndex": 38
    },
    {
      "start": 107.137,
      "end": 109.041,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "believing that you shall receive,",
      "verse": "15:11",
      "lineIndex": 39
    },
    {
      "start": 109.221,
      "end": 111.822,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "with diligence in keeping my commandments,",
      "verse": "15:11",
      "lineIndex": 40
    },
    {
      "start": 112.002,
      "end": 114.603,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "surely these things shall be made known to you.",
      "verse": "15:11",
      "lineIndex": 41
    },
    {
      "start": 115.283,
      "end": 116.955,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Behold, I say to you,",
      "verse": "15:12",
      "lineIndex": 43
    },
    {
      "start": 117.135,
      "end": 120.386,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that the house of Israel was compared to an olive tree",
      "verse": "15:12",
      "lineIndex": 44
    },
    {
      "start": 120.566,
      "end": 122.377,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "by the Spirit of the Lord",
      "verse": "15:12",
      "lineIndex": 45
    },
    {
      "start": 122.557,
      "end": 124.275,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which was in our father;",
      "verse": "15:12",
      "lineIndex": 46
    },
    {
      "start": 124.455,
      "end": 128.031,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and behold are we not broken off from the house of Israel,",
      "verse": "15:12",
      "lineIndex": 47
    },
    {
      "start": 128.211,
      "end": 130.765,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and are we not a branch of the house of Israel?",
      "verse": "15:12",
      "lineIndex": 48
    },
    {
      "start": 131.445,
      "end": 134.278,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And now, the thing which our father means",
      "verse": "15:13",
      "lineIndex": 49
    },
    {
      "start": 134.458,
      "end": 138.173,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "concerning the grafting in of the natural branches",
      "verse": "15:13",
      "lineIndex": 50
    },
    {
      "start": 138.353,
      "end": 140.907,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "through the fullness of the Gentiles, is,",
      "verse": "15:13",
      "lineIndex": 51
    },
    {
      "start": 141.087,
      "end": 142.712,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that in the latter days,",
      "verse": "15:13",
      "lineIndex": 52
    },
    {
      "start": 142.892,
      "end": 145.818,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "when our seed shall have dwindled in unbelief,",
      "verse": "15:13",
      "lineIndex": 53
    },
    {
      "start": 145.998,
      "end": 149.342,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "yes, for the space of many years, and many generations",
      "verse": "15:13",
      "lineIndex": 54
    },
    {
      "start": 149.522,
      "end": 154.027,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "after the Messiah shall be manifested in body to the children of men,",
      "verse": "15:13",
      "lineIndex": 55
    },
    {
      "start": 154.207,
      "end": 158.387,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "then shall the fullness of the gospel of the Messiah come to the Gentiles,",
      "verse": "15:13",
      "lineIndex": 56
    },
    {
      "start": 158.567,
      "end": 161.911,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and from the Gentiles to the remnant of our seed\u2014",
      "verse": "15:13",
      "lineIndex": 57
    },
    {
      "start": 162.591,
      "end": 163.938,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And at that day",
      "verse": "15:14",
      "lineIndex": 58
    },
    {
      "start": 164.118,
      "end": 166.812,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "shall the remnant of our seed know",
      "verse": "15:14",
      "lineIndex": 59
    },
    {
      "start": 166.992,
      "end": 169.546,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that they are of the house of Israel,",
      "verse": "15:14",
      "lineIndex": 60
    },
    {
      "start": 169.726,
      "end": 172.884,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and that they are the covenant people of the Lord;",
      "verse": "15:14",
      "lineIndex": 61
    },
    {
      "start": 173.064,
      "end": 174.689,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and then shall they know",
      "verse": "15:14",
      "lineIndex": 62
    },
    {
      "start": 174.869,
      "end": 177.655,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and come to the knowledge of their forefathers,",
      "verse": "15:14",
      "lineIndex": 63
    },
    {
      "start": 177.835,
      "end": 181.179,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and also to the knowledge of the gospel of their Redeemer,",
      "verse": "15:14",
      "lineIndex": 64
    },
    {
      "start": 181.359,
      "end": 184.331,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which was ministered to their fathers by him;",
      "verse": "15:14",
      "lineIndex": 65
    },
    {
      "start": 184.511,
      "end": 187.715,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "so, they shall come to the knowledge of their Redeemer",
      "verse": "15:14",
      "lineIndex": 66
    },
    {
      "start": 187.895,
      "end": 190.078,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and the very points of his doctrine,",
      "verse": "15:14",
      "lineIndex": 67
    },
    {
      "start": 190.258,
      "end": 193.416,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that they may know how to come to him and be saved.",
      "verse": "15:14",
      "lineIndex": 68
    },
    {
      "start": 194.096,
      "end": 196.372,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And then at that day will they not rejoice",
      "verse": "15:15",
      "lineIndex": 69
    },
    {
      "start": 196.552,
      "end": 199.292,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and give praise to their everlasting God,",
      "verse": "15:15",
      "lineIndex": 70
    },
    {
      "start": 199.472,
      "end": 201.608,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "their rock and their salvation?",
      "verse": "15:15",
      "lineIndex": 71
    },
    {
      "start": 201.788,
      "end": 203.367,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Indeed, at that day,",
      "verse": "15:15",
      "lineIndex": 72
    },
    {
      "start": 203.547,
      "end": 208.005,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "will they not receive the strength and nourishment from the true vine?",
      "verse": "15:15",
      "lineIndex": 73
    },
    {
      "start": 208.185,
      "end": 211.204,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Indeed, will they not come to the true fold of God?",
      "verse": "15:15",
      "lineIndex": 74
    },
    {
      "start": 211.884,
      "end": 213.556,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Behold, I say to you,",
      "verse": "15:16",
      "lineIndex": 75
    },
    {
      "start": 213.736,
      "end": 218.705,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Indeed; they shall be remembered again among the house of Israel;",
      "verse": "15:16",
      "lineIndex": 76
    },
    {
      "start": 218.885,
      "end": 220.603,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "they shall be grafted in,",
      "verse": "15:16",
      "lineIndex": 77
    },
    {
      "start": 220.783,
      "end": 225.195,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "being a natural branch of the olive tree, into the true olive tree.",
      "verse": "15:16",
      "lineIndex": 78
    },
    {
      "start": 225.875,
      "end": 227.918,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And this is what our father means;",
      "verse": "15:17",
      "lineIndex": 79
    },
    {
      "start": 228.098,
      "end": 230.699,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and he means that it will not come to pass",
      "verse": "15:17",
      "lineIndex": 80
    },
    {
      "start": 230.879,
      "end": 233.619,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "until after they are scattered by the Gentiles;",
      "verse": "15:17",
      "lineIndex": 81
    },
    {
      "start": 233.799,
      "end": 237.328,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and he means that it shall come by way of the Gentiles,",
      "verse": "15:17",
      "lineIndex": 82
    },
    {
      "start": 237.508,
      "end": 240.387,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that the Lord may show his power to the Gentiles,",
      "verse": "15:17",
      "lineIndex": 83
    },
    {
      "start": 240.567,
      "end": 244.236,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for the very cause that he shall be rejected of the Jews,",
      "verse": "15:17",
      "lineIndex": 84
    },
    {
      "start": 244.416,
      "end": 245.949,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "or of the house of Israel.",
      "verse": "15:17",
      "lineIndex": 85
    },
    {
      "start": 246.629,
      "end": 249.973,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "So, our father has not spoken of our seed alone,",
      "verse": "15:18",
      "lineIndex": 86
    },
    {
      "start": 250.153,
      "end": 254.24,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "but also of all the house of Israel, pointing to the covenant",
      "verse": "15:18",
      "lineIndex": 87
    },
    {
      "start": 254.42,
      "end": 257.206,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which should be fulfilled in the latter days;",
      "verse": "15:18",
      "lineIndex": 88
    },
    {
      "start": 257.386,
      "end": 260.962,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which covenant the Lord made to our father Abraham, saying:",
      "verse": "15:18",
      "lineIndex": 89
    },
    {
      "start": 261.142,
      "end": 264.532,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "In your seed shall all the kindreds of the earth be blessed.",
      "verse": "15:18",
      "lineIndex": 90
    },
    {
      "start": 265.212,
      "end": 269.159,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And then I, Nephi, spoke much to them concerning these things;",
      "verse": "15:19",
      "lineIndex": 91
    },
    {
      "start": 269.339,
      "end": 270.918,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "yes, I spoke to them",
      "verse": "15:19",
      "lineIndex": 92
    },
    {
      "start": 271.098,
      "end": 274.627,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "concerning the restoration of the Jews in the latter days.",
      "verse": "15:19",
      "lineIndex": 93
    },
    {
      "start": 275.307,
      "end": 277.072,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And I rehearsed to them",
      "verse": "15:20",
      "lineIndex": 94
    },
    {
      "start": 277.252,
      "end": 279.017,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "the words of Isaiah,",
      "verse": "15:20",
      "lineIndex": 95
    },
    {
      "start": 279.197,
      "end": 282.308,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "who spoke concerning the restoration of the Jews,",
      "verse": "15:20",
      "lineIndex": 96
    },
    {
      "start": 282.488,
      "end": 284.624,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "or of the house of Israel;",
      "verse": "15:20",
      "lineIndex": 97
    },
    {
      "start": 284.804,
      "end": 286.801,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and after they were restored",
      "verse": "15:20",
      "lineIndex": 98
    },
    {
      "start": 286.981,
      "end": 288.978,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "they should no more be confused,",
      "verse": "15:20",
      "lineIndex": 99
    },
    {
      "start": 289.158,
      "end": 291.294,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "neither should they be scattered again.",
      "verse": "15:20",
      "lineIndex": 100
    },
    {
      "start": 291.474,
      "end": 294.121,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And then I spoke many words to my brothers,",
      "verse": "15:20",
      "lineIndex": 101
    },
    {
      "start": 294.301,
      "end": 295.787,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "they were pacified",
      "verse": "15:20",
      "lineIndex": 102
    },
    {
      "start": 295.967,
      "end": 298.335,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and humbled themselves before the Lord.",
      "verse": "15:20",
      "lineIndex": 103
    },
    {
      "start": 299.015,
      "end": 301.383,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And then they spoke to me again, saying:",
      "verse": "15:21",
      "lineIndex": 105
    },
    {
      "start": 301.563,
      "end": 304.674,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "What means this thing which our father saw in a dream?",
      "verse": "15:21",
      "lineIndex": 106
    },
    {
      "start": 304.854,
      "end": 306.665,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "What means the tree which he saw?",
      "verse": "15:21",
      "lineIndex": 107
    },
    {
      "start": 307.345,
      "end": 308.831,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And I said to them:",
      "verse": "15:22",
      "lineIndex": 108
    },
    {
      "start": 309.011,
      "end": 311.658,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "It was a representation of the tree of life.",
      "verse": "15:22",
      "lineIndex": 109
    },
    {
      "start": 312.338,
      "end": 313.824,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And they said to me:",
      "verse": "15:23",
      "lineIndex": 110
    },
    {
      "start": 314.004,
      "end": 317.208,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "What means the rod of iron which our father saw,",
      "verse": "15:23",
      "lineIndex": 111
    },
    {
      "start": 317.388,
      "end": 318.921,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that led to the tree?",
      "verse": "15:23",
      "lineIndex": 112
    },
    {
      "start": 319.601,
      "end": 322.48,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And I said to them that it was the word of God;",
      "verse": "15:24",
      "lineIndex": 113
    },
    {
      "start": 322.66,
      "end": 324.936,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and whoso would listen to the word of God,",
      "verse": "15:24",
      "lineIndex": 114
    },
    {
      "start": 325.116,
      "end": 326.834,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and would hold fast to it,",
      "verse": "15:24",
      "lineIndex": 115
    },
    {
      "start": 327.014,
      "end": 328.779,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "they would never perish;",
      "verse": "15:24",
      "lineIndex": 116
    },
    {
      "start": 328.959,
      "end": 331.235,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "neither could the temptations",
      "verse": "15:24",
      "lineIndex": 117
    },
    {
      "start": 331.415,
      "end": 334.201,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and the fiery darts of the adversary",
      "verse": "15:24",
      "lineIndex": 118
    },
    {
      "start": 334.381,
      "end": 336.749,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "overpower them to blindness,",
      "verse": "15:24",
      "lineIndex": 119
    },
    {
      "start": 336.929,
      "end": 339.297,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "to lead them away to destruction.",
      "verse": "15:24",
      "lineIndex": 120
    },
    {
      "start": 339.977,
      "end": 341.927,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "So, I, Nephi, urged them",
      "verse": "15:25",
      "lineIndex": 121
    },
    {
      "start": 342.107,
      "end": 344.568,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "to give heed to the word of the Lord;",
      "verse": "15:25",
      "lineIndex": 122
    },
    {
      "start": 344.748,
      "end": 347.999,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "yes, I urged them with all the energies of my soul,",
      "verse": "15:25",
      "lineIndex": 123
    },
    {
      "start": 348.179,
      "end": 350.78,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and with all the faculty which I possessed,",
      "verse": "15:25",
      "lineIndex": 124
    },
    {
      "start": 350.96,
      "end": 353.793,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that they would give heed to the word of God",
      "verse": "15:25",
      "lineIndex": 125
    },
    {
      "start": 353.973,
      "end": 357.502,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and remember to keep his commandments always in all things.",
      "verse": "15:25",
      "lineIndex": 126
    },
    {
      "start": 358.182,
      "end": 359.668,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And they said to me:",
      "verse": "15:26",
      "lineIndex": 127
    },
    {
      "start": 359.848,
      "end": 363.006,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "What means the river of water which our father saw?",
      "verse": "15:26",
      "lineIndex": 128
    },
    {
      "start": 363.686,
      "end": 365.776,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And I said to them",
      "verse": "15:27",
      "lineIndex": 129
    },
    {
      "start": 365.956,
      "end": 369.067,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that the water which my father saw was filthiness;",
      "verse": "15:27",
      "lineIndex": 130
    },
    {
      "start": 369.247,
      "end": 372.405,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and so much was his mind swallowed up in other things",
      "verse": "15:27",
      "lineIndex": 131
    },
    {
      "start": 372.585,
      "end": 375.325,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that he saw not the filthiness of the water.",
      "verse": "15:27",
      "lineIndex": 132
    },
    {
      "start": 376.005,
      "end": 378.606,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And I said to them that it was an awful gulf,",
      "verse": "15:28",
      "lineIndex": 133
    },
    {
      "start": 378.786,
      "end": 380.69,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which separated the wicked",
      "verse": "15:28",
      "lineIndex": 134
    },
    {
      "start": 380.87,
      "end": 382.542,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "from the tree of life,",
      "verse": "15:28",
      "lineIndex": 135
    },
    {
      "start": 382.722,
      "end": 384.672,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and also from the saints of God.",
      "verse": "15:28",
      "lineIndex": 136
    },
    {
      "start": 385.352,
      "end": 387.442,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And I said to them",
      "verse": "15:29",
      "lineIndex": 137
    },
    {
      "start": 387.622,
      "end": 390.826,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that it was a representation of that awful hell,",
      "verse": "15:29",
      "lineIndex": 138
    },
    {
      "start": 391.006,
      "end": 394.21,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which the angel said to me was prepared for the wicked.",
      "verse": "15:29",
      "lineIndex": 139
    },
    {
      "start": 394.89,
      "end": 397.444,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And I said to them that our father also saw",
      "verse": "15:30",
      "lineIndex": 140
    },
    {
      "start": 397.624,
      "end": 401.757,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that the justice of God did also divide the wicked from the righteous;",
      "verse": "15:30",
      "lineIndex": 141
    },
    {
      "start": 401.937,
      "end": 404.073,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and the brightness of it",
      "verse": "15:30",
      "lineIndex": 142
    },
    {
      "start": 404.253,
      "end": 407.132,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "was like to the brightness of a flaming fire,",
      "verse": "15:30",
      "lineIndex": 143
    },
    {
      "start": 407.312,
      "end": 410.284,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which ascends up to God forever and ever,",
      "verse": "15:30",
      "lineIndex": 144
    },
    {
      "start": 410.464,
      "end": 411.671,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and has no end.",
      "verse": "15:30",
      "lineIndex": 145
    },
    {
      "start": 412.351,
      "end": 413.837,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And they said to me:",
      "verse": "15:31",
      "lineIndex": 147
    },
    {
      "start": 414.017,
      "end": 417.872,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Does this thing mean the torment of the body in the days of probation,",
      "verse": "15:31",
      "lineIndex": 148
    },
    {
      "start": 418.052,
      "end": 420.513,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "or does it mean the final state of the soul",
      "verse": "15:31",
      "lineIndex": 149
    },
    {
      "start": 420.693,
      "end": 423.015,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "after the death of the temporal body,",
      "verse": "15:31",
      "lineIndex": 150
    },
    {
      "start": 423.195,
      "end": 426.306,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "or does it speak of the things which are temporal?",
      "verse": "15:31",
      "lineIndex": 151
    },
    {
      "start": 426.986,
      "end": 428.565,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And then I said to them",
      "verse": "15:32",
      "lineIndex": 152
    },
    {
      "start": 428.745,
      "end": 433.296,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that it was a representation of things both temporal and spiritual;",
      "verse": "15:32",
      "lineIndex": 153
    },
    {
      "start": 433.476,
      "end": 437.191,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for the day should come that they must be judged of their works,",
      "verse": "15:32",
      "lineIndex": 154
    },
    {
      "start": 437.371,
      "end": 443.083,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "indeed, even the works which were done by the temporal body in their days of probation.",
      "verse": "15:32",
      "lineIndex": 155
    },
    {
      "start": 443.763,
      "end": 446.735,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "So, if they should die in their wickedness",
      "verse": "15:33",
      "lineIndex": 156
    },
    {
      "start": 446.915,
      "end": 448.819,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "they must be cast off also,",
      "verse": "15:33",
      "lineIndex": 157
    },
    {
      "start": 448.999,
      "end": 451.46,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "as to the things which are spiritual,",
      "verse": "15:33",
      "lineIndex": 158
    },
    {
      "start": 451.64,
      "end": 453.916,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which are pertaining to righteousness;",
      "verse": "15:33",
      "lineIndex": 159
    },
    {
      "start": 454.096,
      "end": 456.882,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "so, they must be brought to stand before God,",
      "verse": "15:33",
      "lineIndex": 160
    },
    {
      "start": 457.062,
      "end": 459.152,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "to be judged of their works;",
      "verse": "15:33",
      "lineIndex": 161
    },
    {
      "start": 459.332,
      "end": 463.79,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and if their works have been filthiness they must needs be filthy;",
      "verse": "15:33",
      "lineIndex": 162
    },
    {
      "start": 463.97,
      "end": 466.571,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and if they be filthy it must needs be",
      "verse": "15:33",
      "lineIndex": 163
    },
    {
      "start": 466.751,
      "end": 469.723,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that they cannot dwell in the kingdom of God;",
      "verse": "15:33",
      "lineIndex": 164
    },
    {
      "start": 469.903,
      "end": 472.829,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "if so, the kingdom of God must be filthy also.",
      "verse": "15:33",
      "lineIndex": 165
    },
    {
      "start": 473.509,
      "end": 475.274,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "But behold, I say to you,",
      "verse": "15:34",
      "lineIndex": 166
    },
    {
      "start": 475.454,
      "end": 477.776,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "the kingdom of God is not filthy,",
      "verse": "15:34",
      "lineIndex": 167
    },
    {
      "start": 477.956,
      "end": 480.464,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and there cannot any unclean thing",
      "verse": "15:34",
      "lineIndex": 168
    },
    {
      "start": 480.644,
      "end": 482.827,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "enter into the kingdom of God;",
      "verse": "15:34",
      "lineIndex": 169
    },
    {
      "start": 483.007,
      "end": 485.979,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "so there must needs be a place of filthiness",
      "verse": "15:34",
      "lineIndex": 170
    },
    {
      "start": 486.159,
      "end": 488.527,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "prepared for that which is filthy.",
      "verse": "15:34",
      "lineIndex": 171
    },
    {
      "start": 489.207,
      "end": 491.25,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And there is a place prepared,",
      "verse": "15:35",
      "lineIndex": 172
    },
    {
      "start": 491.43,
      "end": 494.959,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "indeed, even that awful hell of which I have spoken,",
      "verse": "15:35",
      "lineIndex": 173
    },
    {
      "start": 495.139,
      "end": 497.647,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and the devil is the preparator of it;",
      "verse": "15:35",
      "lineIndex": 174
    },
    {
      "start": 497.827,
      "end": 500.335,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "so the final state of the souls of men",
      "verse": "15:35",
      "lineIndex": 175
    },
    {
      "start": 500.515,
      "end": 504.044,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "is to dwell in the kingdom of God, or to be cast out",
      "verse": "15:35",
      "lineIndex": 176
    },
    {
      "start": 504.224,
      "end": 506.825,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "because of that justice of which I have spoken.",
      "verse": "15:35",
      "lineIndex": 177
    },
    {
      "start": 507.505,
      "end": 510.477,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "So, the wicked are rejected from the righteous,",
      "verse": "15:36",
      "lineIndex": 178
    },
    {
      "start": 510.657,
      "end": 513.072,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and also from that tree of life,",
      "verse": "15:36",
      "lineIndex": 179
    },
    {
      "start": 513.252,
      "end": 515.388,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "whose fruit is most precious",
      "verse": "15:36",
      "lineIndex": 180
    },
    {
      "start": 515.568,
      "end": 518.215,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and most desirable above all other fruits;",
      "verse": "15:36",
      "lineIndex": 181
    },
    {
      "start": 518.395,
      "end": 521.506,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "yes, and it is the greatest of all the gifts of God.",
      "verse": "15:36",
      "lineIndex": 182
    },
    {
      "start": 521.686,
      "end": 523.869,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And thus I spoke to my brothers.",
      "verse": "15:36",
      "lineIndex": 183
    },
    {
      "start": 524.049,
      "end": 524.885,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Amen.",
      "verse": "15:36",
      "lineIndex": 184
    }
  ]
}